{"tid":1604942,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【自己人都要屌…搞乜鬼呀？！】做乜撚野擺課集會要有「糾察隊」？","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:17:20.000Z","uid":14328,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a916c1a1566ae9bd101f25854d02291c0408f68","tid":1604942,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"我見啲「糾察隊」有中坑有學生，但呢啲唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n示威者秩序井然，有乜野要糾正，有乜野要觀察？<br />\n<br />\n糾察呢個字本身就係針對示威者行為，字義上係假設左示威者行為會出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n糾察隊２０１４年搞散雨革起大台<br />\n點解而家要拎返呢個字出嚟用？<br />\n<br />\n有「義工」唔用<br />\n有「學生護衛隊」唔用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解係要用「糾察隊」呢個針對自己人既字眼？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你叫鬼滅之刃個鬼殺隊我都無咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以原諒我對字眼既執著<br />\n所謂名不正、言不順、事不成<br />\n<br />\n如果外媒／本地媒體報導香港示威者內部有「糾察隊」，而佢又直譯出去，會唔會誤導左示威者形象？"},{"pid":"94c2ee85277b7fb5ab063fa70a89acea2873e4e9","tid":1604942,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e40d3012d687bfbeded2847f119ad61c367a30","tid":1604942,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"重犯2014雨傘錯誤<br />\n話俾政府知我地係自綁手腳既羔羊 <br />\n政府最鐘意你呢D 無bargain power既運動"},{"pid":"d2eb48097f6c8476f5ad18ff5b97f20100bcef21","tid":1604942,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"有不反對通知既活動一定要有糾察<br />\n規定黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16d0c8f746118fd463604cdf7aa38a24db98fa7","tid":1604942,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZ